{
  "stem": "10406.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And younger people that wanted to leave for Palestine, for Israel, at that time were-- were not allowed in a lot of cases by their parents.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "A lot of people, especially the younger generation, the Zionists, you know, could have-- a lot of people could have gotten out, although that wasn't easy because the British didn't let you in there, you know, so it was a-- But I have my own thinking and philosophy about religion that people that want to blame God-- don't blame God, because God didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Like some religious fanatics, idiots, will come out and say that actually God did this to those Jews over there because they weren't good enough, because the German Jews started assimilating, so therefore, all of them had to pay the price.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I made some-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some-- one of my aunts comes to Chelm and finds out through that man that brought me there and that gardener that I went for food lived in Chelm.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They also had to run away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my aunt met that woman gardener.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and she knew from the other guy that I was in the area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Only that guy knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they-- you know, she-- they introduced her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she and that man came to the farm to take me, you know, back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so I told my farmer that I'm leaving.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I never told him I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She says-- he says he liked me because I was a good workhorse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He said good is not for long, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we find out that another aunt, who now lives in Connecticut, is in Russia and cannot come back because she doesn't have any papers.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
